                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1717-18420509 t18420509-1717-punishment-269"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder,</hi>
